saveWebEntityCreationRule

void saveWebEntityCreationRule(WebEntityCreationRule webEntityCreationRule)
                               throws MemoryStructureException,
                                      org.apache.thrift.TException
Adds or updates a single WebEntityCreationRule to the index. If the rule's LRU is empty, it is set as the DEFAULT rule. If there exists already a rule with this rule's LRU, it is updated, otherwise it is created.
